<section class="stack faq">
  <div class="stack faq-header">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p>
      Everything you need to know about training with South Van FC Academy and
      Men's club.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="stack faq-list">
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Who is the men's team for?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div>
          <p>
            The Men's Team is for serious players committed to competing at the
            VMSL Men's Open level. We demand passion, discipline, and a winning
            mentality as we push for promotion each season. Players must be 18+,
            with select younger players considered with parental consent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Does the men's team train?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div>
          <p>
            Yes. Training takes place once per week and is a key part of
            preparing for VMSL competition. Commitment and performance in
            training directly influence match selection and playing time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Who is the academy for?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div>
          <ul class="custom-list">
            <li>Motivated youth players (grassroots to youth development)</li>
            <li>Players who want to improve technically and tactically</li>
            <li>Athletes committed to consistent training and growth</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>What programs do you offer?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <ul class="custom-list">
          <li>
            Technical & Foundation Program with focus on ball mastery,
            coordination, movement
          </li>
          <li>
            Game Development Program with focus on tactics, decision-making,
            game understanding
          </li>
          <li>
            High-Performance Pathway & Exposure for advanced players looking to
            join and get exposure to high level teams
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Do I need to play for South Van FC to join?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>
          No. Players from any club are welcome. The academy is designed to
          supplement club soccer. We are looking to develop our own youth club
          in the future, stay tuned!
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Do you offer trials or evaluations?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>
          Yes. Evaluation sessions help us understand each playerâ€™s technical
          ability, mindset, and development stage, allowing us to place them in
          an environment that supports long-term growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">
        <h3>Where are training sessions held?</h3>
        <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>
          Training locations vary by program and season. All sessions are held
          at approved local fields within the Tri City area. Full details are
          shared after registration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .faq-header {
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .faq-list {
    gap: 15px;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  /* Remove default marker */
  .faq-question {
    list-style: none;
  }
  .faq-question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-question {
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid #013478;
  }
  .faq-question:hover {
    background-color: #ddeeff;
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Icon (plus -> minus) */
  .faq__icon {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    position: relative;
    flex: 0 0 18px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .faq__icon::before,
  .faq__icon::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    margin: auto;
    width: 18px;
    height: 2px;
    background: currentColor;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .faq__icon::after {
    width: 2px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq__icon::after {
    transform: scaleY(0);
  }
</style>
